{% extends "base.twig" %}

{% block title %}Terms & Conditions{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<section class="container mt-5">
    <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>
    <p class="lead">Last updated: {{ "now"|date("F j, Y") }}</p>
    
    <div class="mt-4">
        <h3>1. Booking and Reservation</h3>
        <p>By making a reservation with us, you agree to provide accurate information and comply with our cancellation policies. Reservations are subject to availability and confirmation.</p>
        
        <h3>2. Payment</h3>
        <p>Payment is required at the time of booking unless otherwise specified. We accept major credit cards and other payment methods as indicated on our website.</p>
        
        <h3>3. Cancellation Policy</h3>
        <p>Cancellation policies vary by room type and rate. Please review the specific cancellation policy at the time of booking. Cancellations must be made through our website or by contacting us directly.</p>
        
        <h3>4. Check-in and Check-out</h3>
        <p>Standard check-in time is 3:00 PM and check-out is 11:00 AM. Early check-in and late check-out may be available upon request and subject to availability.</p>
        
        <h3>5. Guest Responsibilities</h3>
        <p>Guests are responsible for their own safety and security, and for any damages caused to hotel property during their stay. Smoking is prohibited in all indoor areas.</p>
        
        <h3>6. Limitation of Liability</h3>
        <p>Hotel & Restaurant shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your stay or use of our services.</p>
        
        <h3>7. Changes to Terms</h3>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of our services constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.</p>
        
        <h3>8. Contact</h3>
        <p>For questions about these Terms, please contact us at legal@hotelrestaurant.com.</p>
    </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}